==政治组织==
*[[安哥拉人民解放运动|安哥拉人民解放运动(MPLA - PT)]]<small> = Movimento Popular da Libertação de Angola - Partido do Trabalho (Popular Liberation Movement of Angola - Labour Party, authoritarian, extreme leftist after independence, primarily ethnic Northern Mbundu people Ambundu, renounced Marxism 26 March 1991)</small>
*[[争取安哥拉彻底独立全国联盟|争取安哥拉彻底独立全国联盟(UNITA)]]<small> = União Nacional para a Independência Total de Angola (National Union for the Total Independence of Angola, authoritarian, social democratic, primarily ethnic Southern Mbundu people Ovimbundu) </small>

